Izitolo elinye iphephandaba eliwuzakwabo waleli okukhulunywe nazo, zinqabile ukuphawula ngalokhu. Kodwa uChris Gilomor oyi-Investment Analyst uthe izitolo eziningii zizophoqeleka ukuthi zenze izinto ebezingahleliwe ukubhekana nokuthi ikusasa alaziwa kulesi sikhathi seCovid-19. â€œKuyinto ejwayelekile ukuthi izimpahla ezingadayisile zifakwe endalini ukuze zisuswe esitokweni kutholakale nemali ezithengwe ngayo,"usho kanje. Umbiko owenziwe abeWorld Economic Forum (WEF) kuleli sonto, uveze ukuthi ukudayiswa kwezimpahla zokugqoka kwehle ngo89% ngoEphreli uma kuqhathaniswa nangonyaka odlule ngesikhathi esifanayo. Impahla bathi imbondelene ezitolo nakumaWarehouse, ngisho nezindawo okugcinwa kuzo izimpahla ezisuke zizoyiswa kwamanye amazwe kugcwele kuyachichima. Kungenzeka futhi eziinye izitolo zezimpahla ziphoqeleke ukuthi zigcine zivala thaqa ngenxa yalokhu. UGilmour uthe akukho sitolo esizokwazi ukuthi sibhekane nale nkinga ngaphandle kokuthi sishayele emalini. Inkampani i-Edcon Holdings Ltd, ingezinye zezinkampani eseziphumele obala zaveza ukuthi zisenkingeni yezimali, zaveza nokuthi zizovalwa ngenxa yalokhu. Kulesi sonto nje kube nesiphakamiso sale nkampani ukuthi sidayise u-Edgars, Jet noThank U Digital Services. Le nkampani iveze ukuthi izama ukuhlela kabusha inkampani ukuze ikwazi ukubhekana nezinkinga ebhekene nazo njengamanje. UGilmour uchazile ukuthi izinkinga zakwa-Edcon, kungenzeka ukuthi zibhebhethekiswe wukuqubuka kwecoronavirus. "Kubantu abaningi kubalulekile ukuthi baphume emakhaya baye ezitolo, kuyingxenye yokuzikhipha,"usho kanje. 